Parameter:
  (<Conference name>)

Description:
  Creates a new conference with the given name. You are also asked
  for the type of conference, open, closed, secret or news.

  An open conference is open for everyone to subscribe to.

  A closed or secret conference is only open to those tho have had
  permissions added by the conference-creator.

  A secret conference is invisible to all others except those who
  have permissions to it.

  A news conference is linked to the usenet-conference by the same
  name. All texts written here is posted as news.

Observe:
  Always make a conference secret if you create it for a special
  group of people and not for a special subject.
